Crypto  Beauty  
Position: 48.95149, 2.44796

â¨ The Beauty radiation was captured on a microchip at this https://goo.gl/maps/bmunqtnejaH6e2gU7

This emochain is beauty produced by someone, connected by radio frequency with this NFT. The artist Arseneca has created a link between the tangible and intangible world. The NFT contains the geographical coordinates from where beauty was created by a star and the Unix time of the moment.  
 An emochain is like a vibrating rope between the two worlds. 
 The reflection in the NFT reveals the moment when the emochain was created
